    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People or corporate bodies who design and construct stained glass works, which are windows or other objects made of glass colored by adding metallic oxides to the molten glass.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
